This disease is getting worse. Today, I awoke and had to fart urgently. I pushed to force the warm gas through my fecal discharge opening. I was horrified when the liquified remains of some unknown internal organs discharged. I cannot move and have been wallowing in the filthy stench of my own necrosis. The only comfort I have is the soothing flavor of Marlboro Country. Imagine an old cardboard box that has been wet. They smell terribly. The box is sitting in the middle of a desert. Nothing but sand and sun as far as the eye can see. Not even the slightest hint of a breeze. Suddenly a bomb detonates inside the box. And so I am.

Today I was visited by two aliens. They said their society had solved all medical problems and they had come to give me this valuable information so that our world could benefit from it. Unfortunately, they both died of some strange Earth disease before they could give me anything. I'm not feeling so well.

Hello, I am Mr. Cabbagehead! I was born late this morning. Unfortunately, my mother smoked during her pregnancy and I was born addicted to nicotine. I made her pay for her sins by cannibalizing her.
